REQUIREMENTS:
-------------

Any Amiga computer manufactured year 1992 or later equipped with 16
megs of ram running 100% compatible AmigaOS.

AGA Chipset or 100% compatible.
2 megs of chipram.
16 megs of fastram.
64 megs of free hard drive space.


Total Chaos only actually uses about 1 meg of chipram and 11 megs of
fastram so if you have an old 16 meg Amiga you should still be able
to play the game while web browsing + IRCing + Emailing etc.



